lass);\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void hiddenImplByClassNameLoadsNonPublicConstructor() {\n        DynConstructors.Ctor<HiddenConstructible> ctor = new DynConstructors.Builder(HiddenConstructible.class)\n                .hiddenImpl(HiddenConstructible.class.getName(), String.class)\n                .build();\n\n        HiddenConstructible instance = ctor.newInstance(\"hidden by name\");\n\n        assertThat(instance.value()).isEqualTo(\"hidden by name\");\n        assertThat(ctor.getConstructedClass()).isEqualTo(HiddenConstructible.class);\n    }\n\n    public static class PublicConstructible {\n        private final String value;\n\n        public PublicConstructible(String value) {\n            this.value = value;\n        }\n\n        String value() {\n            return value;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static class HiddenConstructible {\n        private final String value;\n\n        private HiddenConstructible(String value) {\n            this.value = value;\n        }\n\n        String value() {\n            return value;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 576, "output": 1045, "cacheRead": 11264, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 12885, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777796173196, "responseId": "resp_029d69e5c64d1e1d0169f7044d85388195b1abec09e23a6ba9"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_liy7YvJhxzJrhUw2YfbujTMc|fc_029d69e5c64d1e1d0169f7045544d081958db144932cd930fd", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1958 bytes to tests/src/org.apache.parquet/parquet-common/1.12.2/src/test/java/org_apache_parquet/parquet_common/DynConstructorsInnerBuilderTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777796184303}]}
